                <head>584. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>An agreement between the United States and Venezuela extending the Air Force
                    Mission agreement of January 16, 1953, was effected by an exchange of notes at
                    Washington, February 11 and 15, 1957, and entered into force on the latter date.
                    For text of the notes, see 8 UST 209. Documentation relating to this matter is
                    in Department of State, Central File 731.58.</p>
            </div>
